Method.СформироватьСтруктуруМетаданных.Param.ИмяПланаОбмена.Description=If peredana String, to ona interpretiruetsya As Name Path\nplana Encoding, To kotorogo stroitsya Tree L.\n- If peredan Node Encoding, to Tree L stroitsya To ego Message Encoding.\n- If Parameter neopredelen, to stroitsya Tree vsey L.\nVozvrashchaet Conversion C polyami "StrukturaImen", "StrukturaPredstavleniy", "Tree",\nopisyvayushchuyu Metadata. Objects, Dont vkhodyashchie In Composition Message Encoding, vybrasyvayutsya.\n"StrukturaImen" - Structure, gde Name - Group Path (Constants, spravochniki T Config.P.),\nznachenie - Array polnykh Names.\n"StrukturaPredstavleniy" - Structure, gde Name - Group Path (Constants, spravochniki\ni Config.P.), Value - Array List. Order List  In Array sovpadaet C massivom\npolnykh Names.\n"StrukturaAvtoregistratsii" - Structure, gde Name - Group Path (Constants, spravochniki\ni Config.P.), Value - Array flagov avtoregistratsii To Node. Order Schema In Array sovpadaet\ns massivom polnykh Names. Vkhodyat Only te Group, kotorye Dont vkhodyat In Tree.\n"Tree" - Tree Table, 3 Sets\: Group configuration->Type Form->Object.\nKolonki Standart\:\n- Description        - Presentation Type Form Path\n- MetaPolnoeImya       - Panel Name Form Path\n- PictureIndex      - Zavisit From Path\n- Check             - Neopredeleno\n- IdentifikatorStroki - ZIP dobavlennoy Trailing (obkhod Standart sverkhu Down sleva napravo)\n- Auto register     - If ukazan ImyaPlanaObmena, to To listev\: 1-razreshena, 2-zapreshchena. Inache Neopredeleno\n- KolichestvoIzmeneniy        - Neopredeleno, nuzhno To dalneyshego Tree\n- KolichestvoVygruzhennykh      - Neopredeleno, nuzhno To dalneyshego Tree\n- KolichestvoNevygruzhennykh    - Neopredeleno, nuzhno To dalneyshego Tree\n- KolichestvoIzmeneniyStrokoy - Neopredeleno, nuzhno To dalneyshego Tree
